import Axios from "axios"


const AddAnchorage = (props) => {
	const latitude = props.onAddAnchorage.position.lat
	const longitude = props.onAddAnchorage.position.lng
	const name = props.onAddAnchorage.getName
	const capacityId = props.AddAnchorage.capacityId
	/*const waterDeepId = props.AddAnchorage.waterDeepId
	const windId = props.AddAnchorage.windId
	const bottomId = props.AddAnchorage.bottomId*/

	console.log(latitude, "lat",longitude,"long", name, "name", capacityId,"cap")

		Axios.post("http://localhost:3001/createAnchor", {
			name: name,
			latitude: latitude,
			longitude: longitude,
			capacity: capacityId,
			/*waterDeep: waterDeepId,
			wind: windId,
			bottom: bottomId*/
		}).then(() => console.log("úspěch"))



}

export default AddAnchorage
